<body>

    <h1>The Cowboy Hat Truth Consigliere</h1>
    <p class="tagline">I read your micro-expressions, quote the generals, and tell you "that's fucking dogshit try again" while your team nods politely.</p>

    <img src="YOUR-COWBOY-HAT-PHOTO.jpg" alt="Jacob 'Jack' Ford - Cowboy Hat Truth Consigliere">

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Jacob "Jack" Ford</h2>
        <p>Starving for outside perspective from a slightly autistic polymath?</p>
        <p>You've found the solution — the Truth Time Consigliere.</p>
        <p>With cowboy hat, hoodie, potential chain smoking and casual swearing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Unfiltered Facts</h2>
        <p>I am about the truth. I cannot stand a falsehood, a fallacy, or a corporate lie.</p>
        <p><strong>Here is where corporate lies go to die and the truth lives.</strong></p>
        <p>You don't need to be fluffed up. You're already successful. You need hard facts!</p>
        <p>Think of how many millions and billions corporations have lost to lies and games because nobody said: "that's damned stupid" or "they're a fucking liar." Bud Light. Nuff said.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Lol</h2>
        <p>I call out bullshit from a mile away.</p>
        <p>For deep analysis I leverage many frontier AI models.</p>
        <p>Don't fall victim to yes men and women and sycophants.</p>
        <p><strong>Anti-Yes Man | Truth Time Consigliere</strong></p>
        <p>(Cowboy hat is optional. Hoodie is not optional. Extra fee will apply for suit and tie.)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>KamiLux LLC – Truth Time Consigliere Fee Schedule</h2>

        <h3>90-Min Intention & Blind Spot Audit</h3>
        <p>I'll spot hidden intentions, micro-expressions, and yes-man risks, then deliver the unfiltered truth + fixes.</p>
        <p><strong>Fee: $3,500</strong></p>

        <h3>Truth Time Retainer</h3>
        <p>Monthly consigliere access: unlimited 1:1 sessions, on-call reads, AI-augmented analysis, written truth reports, and direct "that's fucking dogshit — try again" counsel.</p>
        <p><strong>$15,000 / month</strong> (3-month minimum) or <strong>$12,000 / month</strong> (6+ months)</p>

        <h3>Live Meeting / Negotiation Read</h3>
        <p>I join (Zoom or in-person) and read the room in real time.</p>
        <p><strong>Fee: $4,500 per session</strong></p>

        <h3>Team Workshop – "Build Your Own Anti-Yes-Man System"</h3>
        <p>Half-day session training your leaders to spot BS and give/receive hard truth.</p>
        <p><strong>Fee: $12,000</strong> (up to 12 people)</p>

        <h3>Add-Ons</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Suit & Tie Appearance:</strong> +$2,500 (I'll ditch the cowboy hat and hoodie... this time)</li>
            <li><strong>Rush / Same-Week Booking:</strong> +30%</li>
            <li><strong>In-Person (your location):</strong> Travel + lodging at cost</li>
            <li><strong>1 Year Contract Consultancy</strong> (multiple meetings per week + exclusivity of my services): Negotiable</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Preferred Payment Methods</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>ACH / Wire Transfer – Preferred.</li>
            <li>Overnight Cashier's Check via FedEx – Mailed to business address.</li>
            <li>Crypto (BTC preferred or other on request)</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Payment Terms:</strong> Due within 3 business days of invoice. Late fee 1.5% per month. All fees in USD.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section" style="text-align:center; margin-top:60px;">
        <p><strong>You're not hiring me to make your decisions. You're hiring me so you can make the best decisions possible.</strong></p>
        <p><strong>I am the energy. I don't just bring it.</strong></p>
        <p>Questions? Book a quick call or DM me on X <strong>@KamiLuxLLC</strong></p>
        <p><strong>Truth Time starts when you're ready.</strong></p>
    </div>

